Add user defines at the top of the SPEC file
  --define foo 'bar %{xxx}'
would add the line:
   %define  foo   bar %{xxx}

If META has 'provides', make sure that we only use provides for the
files we actually install.

===

This was written using ideas from cpanspec-1.78.

